22#include "gprof.h"
23#include "libiberty.h"
24#include "search_list.h"
25
26
27void
28search_list_append (Search_List *list, const char *paths)
29{
30 Search_List_Elem *new_el;
31 const char *beg, *colon;
32 unsigned int len;
33
34 colon = paths - 1;
35 do
36 {
37 beg = colon + 1;
38 colon = strchr (beg, PATH_SEP_CHAR);
39
40 if (colon)
41 len = colon - beg;
42 else
43 len = strlen (beg);
44
45 new_el = (Search_List_Elem *) xmalloc (sizeof (*new_el) + len);
46 memcpy (new_el->path, beg, len);
47 new_el->path[len] = '\0';
48
49 /* Append new path at end of list. */
50 new_el->next = 0;
51
52 if (list->tail)
53 list->tail->next = new_el;
54 else
55 list->head = new_el;
56
57 list->tail = new_el;
58 }
59 while (colon);
60}
